short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: All the news a programmer could ever need

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Tech Feeds is a chrome extension that is heavily inspired by the now unmaintained Coven app and shows the content of some of the most important tech websites on your new tab screen. It's a new aggregator for Programmers. It shows content from:

- Hacker News
- /r/programming
- Product Hunt

You will always get the most important news headlines from all of these websites right onto your screen whenever you open a new tab. Never miss anything important again!
